caption.text:
Hello People of Tomorrow !
Lack of understanding on how to take care of the reproduction system is a massive problem in Indonesia. Sharing the right way to treat the reproduction system to society is our responsibilty as medical student . 
I, Ignatius Ivan, am giving my full support to Rapat Kerja Nasional of AMSA-Indonesia by AMSA-Unja in Jambi that will be held in Jambi 8th-10th of September 2017 with theme ‚ÄòESTROGEN‚Äô (Establishing your personal hygiene and reproduction) .

I am really optimistic that we, as medical student, can improve and stabilize reproductive health in indonesia.
I wish
- We, as a medical student are more encouraged to spread the importance of having a good reproductive health to our surroundings
- We as the citizen of Indonesia can together build a leading model of great reproductive lifestyle so we can increase a better human resource in the future
- We, as the member of AMSA Indonesia can increase our knowledge and awareness in reproductive health

So, prepare yourself for healthier Indonesia. See you soon in Jambi !
